{"tid":1080442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[做MTR比人打] 港鐵車長中環站遇襲受傷警拘一名男乘客","createTime":"2019-03-27T15:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T00:59:18.000Z","uid":51620,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2de942180b7e327cf1ba93494d1420047113ada1","tid":1080442,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T15:06:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1080950&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1080950%26csid%3D261_341&d=5mmA4sQKuQaI7%2FjJJ4WTlxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=59bf4a38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1080950&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n一名33歲港鐵車長，在荃灣綫中環站2號月台，遭一名48歲男乘客襲擊，胸口及腳部受傷，送往瑪麗醫院治理。警方事後拘捕涉案48歲男乘客，他涉嫌襲擊導致造成身體傷害。<br />\n<br />\n事發下午五時許，事主在中環站車尾準備步行到列車車頭時，發覺有人用腳從背後踼他的腳，轉頭一望時，對方揮拳打他的腹部，其他乘客見到報警及通知車站其他職員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c8191739f2e44aa50f88072208b0f4c76ac5b7","tid":1080442,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T15:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e2f7c42c5ac515e5d43e9cd6632edea9532773","tid":1080442,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T15:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06f549844b52f985c7bd4def4962db14e57e1f3","tid":1080442,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0